前教宗雷定五世，重新恢復為伯多祿·安吉納列奧，他的辭職受到各方反對，樞機貝尼代托·卡爾泰尼欲想成為教宗，但卻有前教宗同時在世，這是非常罕有，他有成為對立教宗之險，於是下令將伯多祿帶回羅馬監視。伯多祿得知消息逃入森林，返回蘇爾莫納繼續修行，他這想法顯然不知嚴重性，亦太天真，貝尼代托的爪牙捉住了他，伯多祿打算逃到[[達爾馬提亞|達爾馬提亞]]，但再次失敗了。貝尼代托·卡爾泰尼將之軟禁在費倫蒂諾的城堡中。伯多祿主要支持者查理二世得知消息，帶同人馬包圍城堡，請求不要辭職，修士和教徒亦遊行集會請求他不要離開職務，但這一次伯多祿堅持立場，不予理會。9日後，[[教宗選舉_(1294年)|教宗選舉]]舉行，選出貝尼代托·卡爾泰尼為新教宗[[波尼法爵八世|波尼法爵八世]]，伯多祿的辭職是不可逆轉了。波尼法爵八世急不及待徹除伯多祿的教令和任命，大量擴張他自己的家族<ref name=Archelaos/>。

軟禁伯多祿約九個月後，他被支持者救出，但被捉回，不久死在那裡，伯多祿的支持者宣稱他是被[[波尼法爵八世|波尼法爵八世]][[謀殺|謀殺]]，[[波尼法爵八世|波尼法爵八世]]將異見鎮壓。伯多祿安葬在軟禁地費倫蒂諾城堡中，後來遷到他的加冕地聖康林馬利奧的瑪麗亞教堂安葬。儘管梵蒂岡一直以來否認雷定五世遭謀殺，但轉移雷定五世葬地時學者發現他的頭骨有指甲大小之裂口，大部份學者都認為他是非正常死亡<ref name=Loughlin1908/><ref name=Archelaos/>。

[[法國國王|法國國王]][[腓力四世_(法蘭西)|腓力四世]]素來支持雷定五世反對[[波尼法爵八世|波尼法爵八世]]，克萊孟五世當選教宗之後腓力四世提名雷定五世為聖人。1313年[[宗教法院|宗教法院]]拜隆納家族勢力壓倒波尼法爵八世的奧爾西尼家族時，雷定五世被冊封聖典，是為聖雷定五世<ref>Finucane, Ronald C. (2011) ''Contested Canonizations''</ref>。

== 遺贈 ==
[[File:Celestino_V_tomba.jpg|left]]

現代比較注意的是雷定五世之辭職<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/3350359/Cardinal-hints-that-ailing-Pope-may-resign.html | title = Cardinal hints that ailing Pope may resign | first = Bruce | last = Johnston | author2 = Jonathan Petre | work = The Telegraph | date = 8 February 2005 | accessdate = 2013-04-01 | archive-date = 2013-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130215074201/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/3350359/Cardinal-hints-that-ailing-Pope-may-resign.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，他為教宗辭職立下法理性依據，有時將他比喻為第一個辭職的教宗，然而早在他之前已有[[教宗彭謙|彭謙]]<ref>{{cite book |last=Mcbrien |first=Richard P. |title=The Pocket Guide to the Popes |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=LD59jfaKEIsC&pg=PA30 |accessdate=6 March 2012 |date=31 October 2006 |publisher=HarperCollins |isbn=978-0-06-113773-0 |pages=30–31 |archive-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616064217/http://books.google.com/books?id=LD59jfaKEIsC&pg=PA30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[本篤九世|本篤九世]]、[[額我略六世|額我略六世]]<ref>Coulombe, Charles A., ''Vicars of Christ: A History of the Popes'', (Citadel Press, 2003), 198.</ref>等教宗辭職，但是卻沒有像雷定五世般沒有外來政治壓力，自願自發地辭職。他最大的功績是恢復額我略十世[[教宗詔書|教宗詔書]]《[[那裡有危機|那裡有危機]]<ref>[http://www.osjcuria.org/sga/young/giovannipaolo/ubipericulum.pdf Latin text of ''Ubi periculum''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064715/http://www.osjcuria.org/sga/young/giovannipaolo/ubipericulum.pdf |date=2016-03-04 }}</ref>》教宗秘密選舉教令，秘密選舉傳統一直傳承到今日<ref name="colomer">Josep M. Colomer and Iain McLean. (1998). "Electing Popes: Approval Balloting and Qualified-Majority Rule". ''The Journal of Interdisciplinary History'', Vol. 29, No. 1, pp. 1-22.</ref>。

1966年[[保祿六世|保祿六世]]訪問雷定五世死亡地費倫蒂諾，演講中向雷定五世表示敬意，《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》猜測保祿六世正考慮為教宗訂立退休政策<ref>Cf. [http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/paul_vi/speeches/1966/documents/hf_p-vi_spe_19660901_s-celestino-v_it.html Pope Paul VI's speech of 1 September 1966] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/paul_vi/speeches/1966/documents/hf_p-vi_spe_19660901_s-celestino-v_it.html |date=20130411013616 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,836464,00.html | title = Roman Catholicism: Retirement for 200 Bishops | work = Time Magazine | date = 30 September 1966 | accessdate = 19 May 2011 | archive-date = 2013-03-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130329152636/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,836464,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。雷定五世遺骸遷到聖康林馬利奧的瑪麗亞教堂，所在地2009年遇上[[2009年拉奎拉地震|拉奎拉地震]]，教堂倒塌但遺骸無損，意大利國家的文物安全委員會負責人表示：「這是另一個偉大的教宗奇蹟<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2009/04/09/Popes-bones-survive-earthquake/UPI-18401239303447/ | date = 9 April 2009 | accessdate = 19 May 2011 | publisher = United Press International | title = Pope's bones survive earthquake | archive-date = 2013-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130318154801/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2009/04/09/Popes-bones-survive-earthquake/UPI-18401239303447 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。」教堂短時間已經重修好<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/apr/14/italian-earthquake-damage | title = Italy earthquake focus shifts to saving Abruzzo's heritage | first = Tom | last = Kington | work = The Guardian | date = 14 April 2009 | accessdate = 19 May 2011 | archive-date = 2009-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090417061305/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/apr/14/italian-earthquake-damage | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2009年4月28日，本篤十六世訪問拉奎拉檢查教堂的損毀情況，雷定五世的遺骸抬出了大廳中間擺放，本篤十六世在玻璃棺前禱告，並把他2005年4月[[教宗就職|教宗就職]]典禮用過的羊毛[[披帶|披帶]]放在棺上作禮物後離去<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/faith/article6184757.ece | title = Pope Benedict XVI visits Abruzzo earthquake zone to pray for victims | first = Richard | last = Owen | work = The Times | date = 28 April 2009 | accessdate = 19 May 2011 | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604182918/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/faith/article6184757.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/29/world/europe/29pope.html | title = Pope visits devastated earthquake zone | first = Rachel | last = Donadio | work = The New York Times | date = 28 April 2009 | accessdate = 25 February 2013 | archive-date = 2017-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171016230132/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/29/world/europe/29pope.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

為了紀念雷定五世誕生800週年，本篤十六世宣佈2009年8月28日至2010年8月29日為「雷定年」<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/secretariat_state/card-bertone/2009/documents/rc_seg-st_20090828_anno-celestiniano_it.html | title = Homily of Card. Tarcisio Bertone for the opening of the Holy Door on the occasion of the Feast of Celestinian Forgiveness and the beginning of the Celestinian Year | publisher = The Roman Curia | language = it | date = 28 August 2009 | accessdate = 19 May 2011 | archive-date = 2013-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130303033402/http://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/secretariat_state/card-bertone/2009/documents/rc_seg-st_20090828_anno-celestiniano_it.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年7月4日本篤十六世參觀拉奎拉附近的[[蘇爾摩納大教堂|蘇爾摩納大教堂]]<ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.romereports.com/palio/benedict-xvi-praised-courage-of-celestine-v-another-pope-who-resigned-english-9014.html| title = Benedict Praised courage of Celestine V, another Pope who resigned| publisher = Rome Reports| language = en| date = 12 February 2013| accessdate = 25 February 2013| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130217232130/http://www.romereports.com/palio/benedict-xvi-praised-courage-of-celestine-v-another-pope-who-resigned-english-9014.html| archivedate = 2013年2月17日}} </ref>，作為雷定年儀式的一部份，本篤十六世將1294年10月10日雷定五世的遺物奉獻祭壇前<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/benedict_xvi/travels/2010/documents/trav_ben-xvi_sulmona_20100704_en.html | title = Pastoral Visit to Sulmona | publisher = The Roman Curia | language = en | date = 4 July 2010 | accessdate = 15 February 2013 | archive-date = 2013-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130303070004/http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/benedict_xvi/travels/2010/documents/trav_ben-xvi_sulmona_20100704_en.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《[[羅馬殉道錄|羅馬殉道錄]]》5月19日條目提到雷定五世，表示：

{{Quote|「在[[拉齊奧|拉齊奧]]近拉奎拉的費倫蒂諾城堡，聖伯多祿·雷定在此誕生，他半生是阿布魯佐修士的領導人，因尊榮和奇蹟而受人崇敬，年近八旬當選教宗，選名雷定五世，但同年離棄職位獨自退隱<ref>[http://catholicnewslive.com/story/26583 A Pope in hell? The curious case of Pope St. Peter Celestine V]</ref>。」}}

== 創作 ==
傳統認為[[但丁·阿利吉耶里|但丁·阿利吉耶里]]在作品《[[神曲|神曲]]·地獄篇》「無所作為者」一詩中不點名譴責雷定五世，他描述自己抵達[[靈薄獄|靈薄獄]]，在神秘的詩句寫道：

{{Quote|<center>「我看出、並且也認得那個人的魂靈，<br />
他就是那曾出於怯懦而放棄重要權位的人。」<br /></center>|<small>《[[神曲|神曲]]·地獄篇》第三章《無所作為者》59至60段</small>}}

《神曲》評注人[[格拉齊奥洛·德·班巴利奥利|格拉齊奥洛·德·班巴利奥利]]1324年引述但丁的兒子[[雅格布·阿利吉耶里|雅格布·阿利吉耶里]]的意見，認為此段含意是指雷定五世<ref>{{Cite book | last = Alighieri | first = Jacopo | title = Chiose alla cantica dell'Inferno | location = Florence | publisher = Tipografica di Tommaso Baracchi | year = 1848 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=JcwFAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA12 | page = 12 | language = it | access-date = 2013-04-01 | archive-date = 2013-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130526224423/http://books.google.com/books?id=JcwFAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，近期的學者[[芭芭拉·雷諾茲|芭芭拉·雷諾茲]]也認為是可能的。弗朗切斯科·彼特拉克不同意但丁指責雷定五世怯懦，篡改移除了詩句。現代學者[[馬克·穆薩|馬克·穆薩]]則認為，但丁可能指其他人，[[以掃|以掃]]、[[戴克里先|戴克里先]]或[[本丟彼拉多|本丟彼拉多]]等等<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://meyerenglishwiki.wikispaces.com/file/view/dante+study+guide.pdf |title=Dante’s Inferno:A Discussion Guide By David Bruce |accessdate=2013-04-01 |archive-date=2013-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228172325/http://meyerenglishwiki.wikispaces.com/file/view/dante+study+guide.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1346年，弗朗切斯科·彼特拉克公開《孤獨的生活》一文，讚頌雷定五世拒絕權力歸隱孤獨<ref>{{Cite book | last = Petrarca | first = Francesco | title = De vita Solitaria | location = Bologna | publisher = Gaetano Romagnoli | year = 1879 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=Lmo9AAAAYAAJ&dq=%22De%20vita%20Solitaria%22%20petrarch&source=gbs_similarbooks | language = it | access-date = 2013-04-01 | archive-date = 2013-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130526235200/http://books.google.com/books?id=Lmo9AAAAYAAJ&dq=%22De%20vita%20Solitaria%22%20petrarch&source=gbs_similarbooks | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[丹·布朗|丹·布朗]]《[[天使與魔鬼|天使與魔鬼]]》第88章引用雷定五世為其中一位遭[[謀殺教宗列表|謀殺教宗]]，[[天使與魔鬼_(電影)|電影版]]亦有相同的描述<ref>[[丹·布朗|丹·布朗]]《[[天使與魔鬼|天使與魔鬼]]》第88章</ref>。

1968年，[[伊格納奇奧·斯隆|伊格納奇奧·斯隆]]將雷定五世一生改編為[[話劇|話劇]]《[[謙遜基督徒的故事|謙遜基督徒的故事]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.qlibri.it/narrativa-italiana/romanzi-storici/l'avventura-di-un-povero-cristiano/ |title=L'avventura di un povero cristiano |accessdate=2013-04-02 |archive-date=2012-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121125203506/http://www.qlibri.it/narrativa-italiana/romanzi-storici/l'avventura-di-un-povero-cristiano/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、1990年[[彼得·巴恩斯|彼得·巴恩斯]]也將雷定五世一生改編為話劇《日落與榮耀》<ref>[http://www.abebooks.com/Sunsets-Glories-Paperback-Peter-Barnes/7696344139/bd Sunsets and Glories (Paperback)]</ref>。

雷定五世的故事〈聖靈的兄弟〉是[[布倫丹·康奈爾|布倫丹·康奈爾]]的故事集《波利克拉的一生和其他童話》其中一篇短篇<ref>{{cite book |title=The Life of Polycrates and Other Stories for Antiquated Children |publisher=Chomu Press |year=2011 |isbn=9781907681042 }}</ref>。

